e EcoTracker monitor reported spot readings every 10 minutes. When using the latest firmware update, the EcoTracker monitor will start averaging every 10 minute reading up until 3 data points have been collected, then will start showing a 30 minute moving average.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-1644_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1646_">What is the service life of the EcoTracker?</span></h3><p class="sc-fXeWAj hLqvjI pf-1647_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1649_">EcoTracker is expected to have a service life of 5 years but this depends on usage conditions, wear tear, etc.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-1650_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1652_">What does the EcoTracker package come with?&nbsp;<br></span></h3><p class="sc-fXeWAj hLqvjI pf-1653_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1655_">EcoTracker package includes the four EcoTracker units along with carrying bag, four power adaptors, four DC extension cables, four step-up cables and product quality certificate.&nbsp;</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-1656_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1658_">What is the return and refund policy?</span></h3><p class="sc-fXeWAj hLqvjI pf-1659_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1661_">We offer returns and refunds within 30 days of the original purchase date. You will be responsible for paying the postage/shipping fees for returning your device. If the device is determined to be defective, you will receive a full refund, and the return shipping fees will be refunded to you by Ecosense.</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-1662_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1664_">What is the data storage capacity of each of the 5-minute, 10-minute sniff mode, and continuous monitoring mode?</span></h3><p class="sc-fXeWAj hLqvjI pf-1665_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1667_">5 minutes sniff mode: 1 month<br>10 minutes sniff mode: 2 month<br>Continuous radon monitoring mode: 1 year</span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-ctqQKy ldqOxu pf-1668_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1670_">Does the EcoTracker come with a battery back-up?&nbsp;</span></h3><p class="sc-fXeWAj hLqvjI pf-1671_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1673_">No. If you would like to use a battery, the EcoTracker requires a 12-volt input. Any standard 5-volt battery pack can also be used, with a 5-volt to 12-volt adapter cable. The required power adapter plug size is 5.5mm x 2.1mm.&nbsp; 20 Ah battery has a 72-hour life while a 30 Ah battery will increase the battery life to approximately 105 hours.</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-fotOHu cVvtTU pf-1674_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fXEqDS hwCMhq pf-1675_"><a href="/products/ecotracker" target="_self" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-hmjpVf eOijaQ pf-1676_ pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1678_">BUY NOW</span></a><a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0106/9911/2511/files/Final_Brochure_ET100_V2.0_compressed.pdf?v=1667949627" target="_blank" data-pf-type="Button" class="sc-hmjpVf eOijaQ pf-1679_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-kiIyQV bOAJVC pf-1681_">EcoTracker Brochure</span></a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-dee9" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-lkgTHX jrzygT pf-1682_"><div style="--cw:1860px" class="sc-fmBCVi iwpzju"><div class="sc-fotOHu cVvtTU pf-1683_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-